<text top="2379" left="1143" width="915" height="41" font="font14" id="p1_t97" reading_order_no="96" segment_no="19" tag_type="text">PAUL  ROBERTSON  (paulr@csail.mit.edu)  is  a  research  scientist  at</text>
<text top="2417" left="1143" width="910" height="46" font="font12" id="p1_t98" reading_order_no="97" segment_no="19" tag_type="text">the  Massachusetts  Institute  of  Technology’s  Computer  Science  and.</text>
